data.description: Bring your toolbelt - great opportunity for a fix and flip or to gain sweat equity! Cute ranch with a finished basement and HUGE backyard - perfect for kids and pets! Sunny, west-facing living room! Eat-in kitchen! 2 sizeable bedrooms share a full bath on the main level! The finished basement features a family room with gas fireplace, 2 bedrooms, a 3/4 bath, and a laundry room! Walk to Highland Hollows Park and Arkansas Elementary School! Plenty of grocery stores, restaurants, Aurora Town Center, I-225, and Buckley Space Force base are just minutes away! Don't miss this fantastic opportunity in Aurora Highlands! ALL OFFERS DUE TODAY THURSDAY 2/22 BY 3PM.
